korea southeast asia and taiwan applied moved into its bowers avenue headquarters in santa clara ca in  managementedit chairman of the board of directors willem p roelandts president and chief executive officer gary e dickerson chief financial officer bob halliday chief technology officer omkaram nalamasu referencesedit  a b c d e applied materials announces fourth quarter and fiscal year  results applied materials inc  november    applied materials about  applied materials inc bloomberg lp retrieved  march   turner tyya n  june  vault guide to the top manufacturing employers vault p  isbn  retrieved  may    mccaffery richard  december  tmf interview with applied materials chairman and chief executive james morgan the motley fool retrieved  april    wheelwright steven c  managing new product and process development text cases simon and schuster p  isbn  retrieved  may    us chip firm constructs rd center in japan computerworld  october  retrieved  april    applied materials expands presence in china solid state technology  october  retrieved  april    a b tsai terence cheng borshiuan  january  the silicon dragon hightech industry in taiwan edward elgar publishing p  isbn  retrieved  april    scientologizing forbes september   p    applied materials buys orbot instruments opal for  mln opal chairman meny erad this is a great day for israeli hightech globes  november  archived from the original on  january    applied materials inc inc august  quarterly report form q filing date august   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved dec       lim louisa  december  the green rush is on in china npr retrieved  may    applied materials to buy varian    httpswwwwsjcomarticlesappliedmaterialsandtokyoelectronpicketerisforpostmergername  httpswwwnytimescombusinessdealbookmakersofchipgearcalloffbillionmergerhtmlreftopicsr  shields anne  january  overview of applied materials silicon systems segment market realist retrieved  april    pimentel benjamin bartash jeffry  november  applied materials